and I kind of promised
Donna my soul.

34:24.230 --> 34:25.527
- That's why
I told your friends

34:25.560 --> 34:27.858
I didn't want anything
to do with her.

34:27.889 --> 34:29.654
- You can't wash
your hands of this.

34:29.699 --> 34:32.795
Please. At least tell me
where to find her.

34:37.199 --> 34:39.339
- Look...

34:39.370 --> 34:42.829
even if I knew, I would
advise you to just stay away.

34:42.880 --> 34:44.541
- And what?

34:44.580 --> 34:46.708
I just wait around for her
creepy ass door to show up?

34:46.750 --> 34:48.377
- What do you mean "her" door?

34:48.420 --> 34:51.047
- I brought 2 people back
with me from limbo.

34:51.080 --> 34:53.742
And when they died,
they both got the same door.

34:53.790 --> 34:55.315
(Scoffs)

34:55.360 --> 34:57.010
- That's impossible.

34:57.060 --> 35:00.519
I mean, from what I understand,
a door is your portal.

35:00.560 --> 35:04.190
If the same door is appearing
to several different people,

35:04.230 --> 35:06.369
it's not leading
to the next world.

35:06.400 --> 35:08.698
It's leading to somewhere
in this world,

35:08.740 --> 35:10.697
somewhere Donna
wants you to go.

35:10.740 --> 35:13.232
- Well, yeah, that I get.
She owns my soul.

35:13.270 --> 35:15.034
But why my friends?

35:15.080 --> 35:16.707
- No, it isn't right.

35:16.740 --> 35:18.947
- Can [...
Can I ignore it?

35:18.980 --> 35:20.903
Can I just live
as a ghost?

35:20.950 --> 35:22.577
- No. She'll know
you're on to her.

35:22.620 --> 35:25.419
Donna wouldn't make a door
you could avoid.

35:25.450 --> 35:28.215
But if you go through the door,
and you are ready for her,

35:28.260 --> 35:29.580
you might have a chance.

35:29.620 --> 35:31.429
- Me against Donna?

35:31.460 --> 35:33.383
This woman makes
buildings disappear.

35:33.430 --> 35:35.421
How do I have any chance
against her?

35:35.460 --> 35:38.862
- Don't underestimate yourself.
You are incredibly powerful.

35:38.900 --> 35:41.062
- Do you mean
Harry Potter powerful

35:41.100 --> 35:43.967
or "you want to make me feel
good about myself" powerful?

35:44.000 --> 35:45.764
- You survived an exorcism.

35:45.810 --> 35:47.460
You made it back
from the dead.

35:47.510 --> 35:50.571
You rescued 2 other souls
and brought them back with you.

35:50.610 --> 35:53.079
I never knew you your
first time on this plane,

35:53.110 --> 35:55.477
but it seems you're
a much different spirit now.

35:55.520 --> 35:57.477
- Yeah...

35:58.490 --> 35:59.912
(Sighs)

36:01.790 --> 36:03.110
How do I get ready?

36:03.160 --> 36:05.254
- Before you become
a ghost again,

36:05.290 --> 36:06.951
resolve any issues
you have in this life.

36:06.990 --> 36:09.960
You don't wanna be weighed down
like you were the first time.

36:10.000 --> 36:11.968
- What do I do when
I actually see Donna?

36:12.000 --> 36:13.820
- You take the power
away from her.

36:13.870 --> 36:15.998
- Love the sentiment.
Need some specifics.

36:16.040 --> 36:17.860
- OK, um...

36:17.900 --> 36:21.803
This is not exactly
my area of expertise,

36:21.840 --> 36:23.535
but...

36:27.710 --> 36:29.018
(Sighs)

36:29.050 --> 36:30.518
How's your Latin?

36:47.400 --> 36:50.165
- So let's cut to the chase.

36:50.200 --> 36:53.500
Is this gonna be
state or federal?

36:53.540 --> 36:55.235
- What?

36:55.280 --> 36:58.341
- Well, every time you drop by
out of the blue like this,

36:58.380 --> 37:02.374
usually it's followed by
some sort of criminal request.

37:02.420 --> 37:04.548
Just trying to plan
my jail time accordingly.

37:04.590 --> 37:06.740
What am I looking at?

37:06.790 --> 37:09.589
- I didn't come here
to ask for anything.

37:09.620 --> 37:11.782
I'm here to say goodbye...

37:12.790 --> 37:14.258
for good.

37:17.930 --> 37:21.560
- I'm sorry.
You know, I, um...

37:21.600 --> 37:23.591
I really wanted to help.

37:24.710 --> 37:26.530
I really wanted this
to work out.

37:26.570 --> 37:29.699
- Well, listen,
had you been more accepting

37:29.740 --> 37:33.870
of my rotting body and my
witness-protection lifestyle,

37:33.910 --> 37:37.210
I mean, we could've
had something real great.

37:37.250 --> 37:38.581
I don't know.

37:38.620 --> 37:40.384
- I mean, I tried.

37:40.420 --> 37:44.084
- I'm joking. Nervously.

37:44.120 --> 37:48.057
The fact that you actually
did try to make this work

37:48.090 --> 37:50.320
says everything about you.

37:51.570 --> 37:53.220
You're everything
I wish I could have had

37:53.270 --> 37:54.999
when I was truly alive.

38:02.180 --> 38:07.107
* The burning of
the solemn fire *

38:08.620 --> 38:11.612
* I could not speak

38:11.650 --> 38:15.280
* For my own state of mind...

38:16.320 --> 38:17.856
- You look better.

38:20.160 --> 38:21.992
Do I wanna know why?

38:23.330 --> 38:25.469
- Probably not.
- Hmm...

38:25.500 --> 38:28.128
* To know

38:28.170 --> 38:31.037
* That your pain is mine *

38:33.170 --> 38:34.831
(Groans)

38:37.010 --> 38:38.705
(Sighs)

38:53.360 --> 38:54.850
(Sighs)

39:05.570 --> 39:07.038
- What do you want?

39:08.740 --> 39:10.674
(Groaning)

39:10.710 --> 39:12.371
- You.

39:18.250 --> 39:21.220
- I'm so hungry.

39:26.260 --> 39:28.058
- What the hell are you?

39:31.770 --> 39:33.761
(Coughing)

39:49.120 --> 39:50.372
(Aidan screams)

39:59.930 --> 40:03.093
- Why did you do this to me?

40:06.930 --> 40:09.137
(Breathing heavily)

40:11.270 --> 40:12.931
<i>Jeff Weston.
Nice 10 meet you.</i>

40:17.780 --> 40:20.806
- It was a lot to take.
Emily will come around.

40:20.850 --> 40:22.579
- You don't know her
like I do.

40:22.620 --> 40:25.920
She's surprisingly stubborn
for a slacker.

40:27.320 --> 40:32.156
- So our small wedding
just got a little smaller.

40:33.630 --> 40:36.793
- This is so far from the
wedding I wanted to give you.

40:38.470 --> 40:42.964
It's not the way I wanted
to start our life together.

40:44.540 --> 40:46.338
- It's OK.

40:46.370 --> 40:49.305
- Is it?
Objectively speaking?

40:49.340 --> 40:53.277
I mean, my sister hates me.
Liam wants us dead.

40:53.310 --> 40:55.950
And if I learned anything
from Sadie the stripper,

40:55.980 --> 40:58.347
it's that Aidan's
strongly worded warning

40:58.380 --> 41:00.189
may not carry
that much weight.

41:00.220 --> 41:03.155
- All I need for the
perfect wedding is you.

41:09.560 --> 41:12.461
Just don't let Sally eat me
before we say "I do."

41:12.500 --> 41:13.820
- Mmm...

41:31.890 --> 41:34.712
- Why did you do this to me?

41:34.760 --> 41:37.559
* You don't

41:38.160 --> 41:42.358
* Need a reason

41:43.800 --> 41:47.521
* For I know that

41:47.570 --> 41:51.359
* What I've done is wrong...

41:51.400 --> 41:53.061
- Hello?

41:54.070 --> 41:56.903
* Yeah it's the same

41:58.310 --> 42:02.372
* Right or wrong

42:04.590 --> 42:08.914
* Yeah it's the same thing

42:09.960 --> 42:13.089
* Right or wrong...

42:14.130 --> 42:15.450
(Gasps)

42:16.460 --> 42:18.792
Please let me go.

42:18.830 --> 42:20.821
- What did you tell the girl?
- Nothing.

42:20.870 --> 42:22.167
- Donna thinks otherwise.

42:22.200 --> 42:23.998
- Donna has taken
so much already.

42:24.040 --> 42:25.508
Just leave the girl alone!

42:27.040 --> 42:30.237
Whatever spirit possesses
this man, I banish you--

42:30.280 --> 42:32.203
(Bones cracking, thud)

42:33.250 --> 42:35.014
(Scoffs)

42:35.050 --> 42:37.371
- You picked
the losing side, lady.

42:37.620 --> 42:41.887
* And both sides are even

42:47.560 --> 42:50.393
* They are even

42:52.070 --> 42:54.869
* And alone *
